
Register a user → POST http://localhost:5000/api/users/register

Login → POST http://localhost:5000/api/users/login

Create Post → POST http://localhost:5000/api/posts

Get All Posts → GET http://localhost:5000/api/posts

Get Posts by User → GET http://localhost:5000/api/posts/user/:userId

Get Single Post → GET http://localhost:5000/api/posts/:id

Update Post → PUT http://localhost:5000/api/posts/:id

Delete Post → DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/posts/:id
